messages.message: @Steve Jenner what is the status of the UK Paystubs and UK Bank Statements apps please? @Harry needs to know
@Shubham @Nithin @avi can you share the latest update on the delivery of these apps?

UK Paystub is published in Prod: https://aihub.instabase.com/hub/apps/2359e246-3b79-4a12-8b1f-d4cac8cf09ea

UK Bankstatement is in Development and target to publish in prod by mid of next week. Will update the thread once its published.

Let me know if more details required.
